{"tid":1366205,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(菲律賓總統) 杜特爾特：「中共」軍事力量太強，我別無選擇","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:28:59.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":135,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"f0396b432cb81ce632d6beb1069385f883731393","tid":1366205,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:36:35.000Z","msg":"被某D連登仔稱為「菲律賓侵侵」既杜特爾特, 做左強人咁耐, 竟決定向中共退讓..... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20190723/rodrigo-duterte-philippines-congress/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fasia-pacific%2F20190723%2Frodrigo-duterte-philippines-congress%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9xxVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=6cededd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20190723/rodrigo-duterte-philippines-congress/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n杜特蒂為對華政策辯護：面對軍事力量別無選擇<br />\nJASON GUTIERREZ<br />\n2019年7月23日<br />\n<br />\n馬尼拉&mdash;&mdash;週一，菲律賓總統羅德里戈&middot;杜特蒂(Rodrigo Duterte)在國會發表年度演說，為其政府願與中國和解的立場及其有爭議的毒品戰進行辯護。毒品戰已致6600多人死亡。<br />\n最近，杜特蒂在對華政策上特別受到批評。上個月他聲稱，面對北京的軍事實力，他在維護國家主權方面幾乎無能為力，由此引發了大規模抗議。<br />\n<br />\n週一，他告訴國會議員，與北京打交道迫使他「做出微妙的平衡」。<br />\n<br />\n杜特蒂於2016年上台，其六年任期已經過半。在演講中，他誇耀了自己取得的各種成就，包括反腐工作和減少官僚作風的舉措。杜特蒂上週還簽署了一項有關性騷擾的里程碑式法律，以及一項同叛亂分子最終達成的和平協議，在該國動盪的南部建立一個自治的穆斯林家園。但有關該國與中國的緊張關係以及毒品戰爭引發的爭議，為他的成就蒙上了陰影。<br />\n<br />\n「我們正在進入一個承擔後果的時期，」杜特蒂說。「在我的前半個任期內，我們做了什麼，應該做卻沒有做什麼，這些都會帶來後果。我對此承擔全部責任。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>公眾因為一艘中國船隻撞上一條菲律賓漁船，致22名漁民在海上漂流直到被一艘越南船隻救起，而感到憤怒無比。杜特蒂對這一事件做了淡化處理。</strong><br />\n<br />\n「打響戰爭會增加悲傷和痛苦，」他說。「戰爭會留下寡婦和孤兒。我不準備也不打算接受更多破壞，如果爆發戰爭，就算規模有限，也會有更多的寡婦和孤兒。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>他說，更好的效果發生在「會議室的私密環境裡，而不是在公共領域的爭吵中」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於此，杜特蒂說，他決心採取和平行動，並且「牢記民族自豪感和領土完整正處於危險之中」。<br />\n<br />\n中菲關係緊張很大程度上源於兩國在南中國海的領土主張。杜特蒂表示，<strong>他在上任之初就曾向中國國家主席習近平提起領土爭端，但中國領導人警告他，就這個問題施壓可能「意味著麻煩」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>杜特蒂說，中國已經在南中國海部署了導彈，可以在幾分鐘內抵達菲律賓首都馬尼拉。<br />\n「你想打仗嗎？」他這個問題顯然是針對民族主義團體的。他說，接到習近平這樣的警告之後，「我還能做什麼?」</strong><br />\n<br />\n他似乎還指責他的前任貝尼尼奧&middot;S&middot;阿基諾三世(Benigno S. Aquino III)失去了斯卡伯勒淺灘（Scarborough Shoal，中國稱之為黃岩島&mdash;&mdash;譯註），中國和菲律賓都聲稱對其擁有主權。他說，2012年，面對中國的封鎖，阿基諾三世讓菲律賓海岸警衛隊撤出了該地區，從而令北京接管了這座島嶼。<br />\n<br />\n在阿基諾任內，菲律賓向海牙的一個國際法庭提起了訴訟，該法院在2016年駁回了中國的領土主張，即它擁有對南海大部分海域的歷史性權利。<strong>但杜特蒂並沒有向中國施壓，要求它接受這個裁決，反而經常訪問北京以緩和關係，並爭取到了數十億美元的投資承諾。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>週一，他向國會表示，即使派遣菲律賓軍隊把中國人趕出有爭議的海域，「我向你們保證，他們不會活著回來。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓小漁民組織全國聯合會(Pamalakaya)主席費爾南多&middot;希卡普(Fernando Hicap)批評杜特蒂的言論是在「挑起戰爭」，他說，保護菲律賓的利益應該是一個國家政策的問題。<br />\n<br />\n「沒有人願意與別國開戰，」希卡普說。「我們要求的是正義，以及菲律賓漁民的權利在我們自己的海域得到尊重。」<br />\n<br />\n他還說，「堅持我們的權利並不等於向侵略者宣戰。」<br />\n<br />\n希卡普表示，對於杜特蒂所承諾的「在適當的時候」對中國採取更強硬態度，廣大漁民並不滿意。他認為，國際法庭的裁決應該立即得到執行。<br />\n<br />\n「解決這一爭端現在恰當其時，」他說。<br />\n<br />\n在國內方面，杜特蒂表示，他將繼續禁毒戰，儘管人權組織表示，這麼做的代價會很高。菲律賓今年早些時候退出了國際刑事法院(International Criminal Court)的初步調查。本月，經成員國投票，聯合國人權理事會(United Nations Human Rights Council)就此事展開調查。<br />\n杜特蒂開玩笑說，只要他能獲得一間「舒適的牢房」和「無限次」的配偶探視，哪怕自己因那些死於毒品戰的人而入獄也不怕。<br />\n<br />\n他還表示，那些因執行他的命令而「被不公正起訴」的警察和士兵將獲得免費法律援助。他沒有提到去年底三名警察因謀殺一名被誤作毒販的青少年而定罪。<br />\n<br />\n杜特蒂發表講話時，觀眾席裡坐著副總統萊妮&middot;羅布雷多(Leni Robredo)，她與包括數名參議員和其他政治反對派成員在內的數十人，上週被控犯有煽動叛亂及其他罪行。他們被控參與了削弱杜特蒂政府的陰謀，而他們稱，這些指控是總統企圖恐嚇批評者，讓他們保持沉默。<br />\n外界原本預計在杜特蒂發表演講期間會出現大批抗議者，但大雨令人數有所減少，不過仍有數千人留在國會附近的街道。他們包括學生、左派人士和修女，其中許多人舉著反杜特蒂的標語，燒毀他的肖像。抗議人群而後和平地散去。"},{"pid":"0ae015416a05e82000424d655de1ec3653f32fb5","tid":1366205,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"昨天，菲律賓總統發言人勸越南在南海問題不要與中共對抗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mb.com.ph/2019/07/24/palace-wary-of-vietnam-china-standoff-at-south-china-sea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mb.com.ph%2F2019%2F07%2F24%2Fpalace-wary-of-vietnam-china-standoff-at-south-china-sea%2F&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9xxVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=2d06263a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mb.com.ph/2019/07/24/palace-wary-of-vietnam-china-standoff-at-south-china-sea/</a><br />\n<br />\nPalace wary of Vietnam-China standoff at South China Sea<br />\nPublished July 24, 2019, 8:07 PM<br />\n<br />\nVietnam might be putting the lives of its people in danger amid the reported standoff with China in the disputed South China Sea, a Palace official said Wednesday.<br />\n<br />\nPresidential Spokesman Salvador Panelo said pursuing peaceful dialogue remains the &ldquo;best&rdquo; method instead of the use of force to address any territorial conflict.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;It means also that Vietnam is risking an armed hostility between the two countries and risking the lives of their people,&rdquo; Panelo said in an interview with reporters at the Palace. &ldquo;There is always a risk of something disastrous,&rdquo; he added.<br />\n<br />\nFor the Philippines, Panelo said President Duterte would not endanger the Filipinos and instead would engage in diplomatic negotiations to deal with the territorial dispute with China.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Rather than risk, the best method to solve the problem is through negotiation, diplomatic negotiations,&rdquo; he said.<br />\n<br />\nPanelo made the comment amid reports that Vietnamese and Chinese ships are locked in a standoff near an offshore oil block in the disputed waters in the South China Sea.<br />\n<br />\nVietnam has reportedly urged China to stop the alleged unlawful activities and remove the oil exploration ship from its territorial waters.<br />\n<br />\nLike Vietnam, the Philippines is also locked in a territorial dispute with China in the same vital waterway.<br />\n<br />\nRecently, the President drew criticisms from some groups for his alleged soft stance in asserting the country&rsquo;s ownership of the West Philippine Sea.<br />\n<br />\nThe President, in his State of the Nation Address, insisted that the West Philippine Sea is &ldquo;ours&rdquo; but the government would not resort to war to drive away China from the territory due to concern of loss of life.<br />\n<br />\nDuterte said while the country owns the West Philippine Sea, China which has installed missiles in the area was &ldquo;in possession&rdquo; of the property.<br />\n<br />\nPanelo has defended the President&rsquo;s statement, saying China has &ldquo;legal and constructive possession&rdquo; of the South China Sea amid its military installations in the area.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;They are positionally in advantage kasi nga marami silang military [because they have a huge military] so there is no contradiction between position and possession,&rdquo; he said.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Possession and position are the same because they are in constructive possession by reason of the position and control of the military installations there,&rdquo; he added."},{"pid":"4bc0c9d4eef1f9b8df705c44bcac517d95ec2643","tid":1366205,"uid":137569,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:39:43.000Z","msg":"投資承諾<br />\nOn9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7858db9ad0fead5a0e694f4056537bbd00d6726a","tid":1366205,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56acaf08025809c11029b5c8f482a1f83c1e1481","tid":1366205,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:42:29.000Z","msg":"強人軟了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb7aca419fb093fb8579bf664c025d9d36aaa2d","tid":1366205,"uid":38518,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家唔使理"},{"pid":"7776be9243513e8fe753be50db7b9b14d48fa30d","tid":1366205,"uid":137217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:42:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"a6cd213229c6d320eb3329c38935a6b88c903786","tid":1366205,"uid":13